<h4><a href="https://www.npr.org/2020/08/10/901014658/aquarium-is-washing-old-wishes-to-pay-bills-during-pandemic">水族馆停摆，挖出游客许愿投下的硬币来付账单</a></h4>
<p><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-1358348" src="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/117342254_10157805290729067_4249345519345615183_o_meitu_1.jpg" alt="" width="1000" height="664" srcset="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/117342254_10157805290729067_4249345519345615183_o_meitu_1.jpg 1000w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/117342254_10157805290729067_4249345519345615183_o_meitu_1-360x239.jpg 360w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/117342254_10157805290729067_4249345519345615183_o_meitu_1-768x510.jpg 768w" sizes="(max-width: 1000px) 100vw, 1000px" /></p>
<p>NPR 消息，美国北卡罗来纳州水族馆因疫情仍在无限期停业中。在这期间，他们从其中一个游客喜欢投币许愿的景点清理出 100 加仑（约 0.38 立方米）的硬币，并邀请网友猜这里面一共有多少钱。这笔钱将用于水族馆在停业期间的维护。</p>
<p>疫情期间，由于外出消费的人减少了，美国的沃尔玛等商超出现了零钱短缺，出于无奈只能要求顾客支付「正好」的现金或要求顾客使用信用卡支付。</p>
<h4><a href="https://hypebeast.cn/2020/8/hey-tea-adidas-zx-7000-fz4401-release-date">阿迪达斯和喜茶联名推出「多肉葡萄」球鞋</a></h4>
<p><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-1358349" src="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/hey-tea-adidas-zx-7000-fz4401-release-date-1.jpg" alt="" width="1280" height="853" srcset="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/hey-tea-adidas-zx-7000-fz4401-release-date-1.jpg 1280w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/hey-tea-adidas-zx-7000-fz4401-release-date-1-360x240.jpg 360w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/hey-tea-adidas-zx-7000-fz4401-release-date-1-768x512.jpg 768w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/hey-tea-adidas-zx-7000-fz4401-release-date-1-1024x682.jpg 1024w" sizes="(max-width: 1280px) 100vw, 1280px" /></p>
<p>Hypebeast 消息，阿迪达斯和喜茶联手以「多肉葡萄」为灵感推出一款合作球鞋。</p>
<p>这是 adidas Originals 以「元素周期表」为主题的「A-ZX」系列中的「Ht」作品。</p>
<h3><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-1293890" src="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/12/wangyo.png" alt="" width="1029" height="180" srcset="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/12/wangyo.png 1029w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/12/wangyo-360x63.png 360w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/12/wangyo-768x134.png 768w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/12/wangyo-1024x179.png 1024w" sizes="(max-width: 1029px) 100vw, 1029px" /></h3>
<h4>高考生暑期扎堆割双眼皮</h4>
<p>高考结束后，淮安市第一人民医院医疗美容科出现高考生扎堆做双眼皮手术现象。很多高考生都利用暑期到医院割双眼皮让自己变美。主任医师万能医生介绍，接诊量是平时的 3-4 倍，其中男生占比 20%。</p>
<p>网友：「变美嘛，又不是什么大手术。我觉得能支持孩子这么做的家长很棒。」「如果所有人都认为只有双眼皮才美，那就有问题了。」「只有我一个去学车吗？」</p>
<h3><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-1293891" src="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/12/shie.png" alt="" width="1715" height="300" srcset="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/12/shie.png 1715w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/12/shie-360x63.png 360w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/12/shie-768x134.png 768w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/12/shie-1024x179.png 1024w" sizes="(max-width: 1715px) 100vw, 1715px" /></h3>
<p><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-1358350" src="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/813.jpg" alt="" width="678" height="779" srcset="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/813.jpg 678w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/813-360x414.jpg 360w" sizes="(max-width: 678px) 100vw, 678px" /></p>
<p>1959 年 8 月 13 日，世界上第一辆装备有三点式安全带的汽车——沃尔沃 PV544 交付使用。</p>
<p>百年汽车发展史中，安全带技术可谓是最有深远意义的技术之一。安全带最早出现在汽车上，是源自于汽车比赛，1922 年开始就有赛车使用简单的皮带来充当「安全带」。1958 年，SAAB 萨博汽车的 GT750 首次标配了安全带，但此时的安全带仍然是两点式的设计，安全性仍有待提高。曾经的飞机工程师尼尔斯·布林（Nils Bohlin）在加入沃尔沃汽车公司之后，于 1959 年推出了「三点式安全带」。他认为，只有一边横跨胸部，一边横跨腰下臀部，从同一固定点由上往下紧扣，方能固牢整个身体。在这样的理念下，他设计了单手就能稳扣的「三点式安全带」。</p>
<p>「我们不好意思通过安全带的专利来收费，因为安全无价。」之后拥有三点式安全带专利的沃尔沃宣布，将这一专利向全世界无偿开放，三点式安全带成为如今几乎所有车辆当中的安全标配。爱范儿提醒：上车之后，无论前后排座位，请切记系好安全带。</p>
<h3><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-1357582" src="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/thur.png" alt="" width="1029" height="153" srcset="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/thur.png 1029w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/thur-360x54.png 360w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/thur-768x114.png 768w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/thur-1024x152.png 1024w" sizes="(max-width: 1029px) 100vw, 1029px" /></h3>
<h4><a href="https://www.apple.com/newsroom/2020/07/apple-central-world-opens-friday-in-thailand/">Apple Central World @ 泰国曼谷</a></h4>
<p><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-1358360" src="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/apple_nso-bangkok_ratchaprasong_07282020.jpg" alt="" width="2000" height="1333" srcset="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/apple_nso-bangkok_ratchaprasong_07282020.jpg 2000w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/apple_nso-bangkok_ratchaprasong_07282020-360x240.jpg 360w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/apple_nso-bangkok_ratchaprasong_07282020-768x512.jpg 768w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/apple_nso-bangkok_ratchaprasong_07282020-1024x682.jpg 1024w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p>
<p>苹果于泰国的第二家直营店 Apple Central World 近日开幕。</p>
<p>这是苹果首家采用全玻璃设计的直营店。在门店内，中间设置了巨大的圆柱形木质结构，迎上「长」出一个平坦的圆形「树冠」。</p>
<p><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-1358361" src="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/apple_nso-bangkok_freestanding-displays_07282020.jpg" alt="" width="2000" height="1514" srcset="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/apple_nso-bangkok_freestanding-displays_07282020.jpg 2000w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/apple_nso-bangkok_freestanding-displays_07282020-360x273.jpg 360w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/apple_nso-bangkok_freestanding-displays_07282020-768x581.jpg 768w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/apple_nso-bangkok_freestanding-displays_07282020-1024x775.jpg 1024w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p>
<p>顾客可从围绕着木结构的螺旋楼梯上下楼，或是乘坐由镜面抛光包覆的电梯穿行于上下两层。</p>
<p><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-1358362" src="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/apple_nso-bangkok_spiral-staircase_07282020.jpg" alt="" width="2000" height="2667" srcset="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/apple_nso-bangkok_spiral-staircase_07282020.jpg 2000w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/apple_nso-bangkok_spiral-staircase_07282020-360x480.jpg 360w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/apple_nso-bangkok_spiral-staircase_07282020-768x1024.jpg 768w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p>